# ğŸ§  Legal Mate Edge â€“ Real-Time AI Legal Companion on NVIDIA Jetson

**Legal Mate Edge** is a cutting-edge GenAI-powered legal assistant that runs fully on-device using the **Gemma 3n LLM** and **NVIDIA Jetson** platform. It enables offline legal clause analysis, OCR-powered document scanning, and intelligent contract feedbackâ€”all in real-time on a portable, secure, and cost-efficient edge device.

